      • deleteLocation

        @RequestMapping(value="/deleteLocation",
                method=POST)
public String deleteLocation(String macAddress,
                                                                                                   String startDate,
                                                                                                   String starthours,
                                                                                                   String startminutes,
                                                                                                   String startseconds,
                                                                                                   String endDate,
                                                                                                   String endhours,
                                                                                                   String endminutes,
                                                                                                   String endseconds,
                                                                                                   String locationID,
                                                                                                   String semanticPlace,
                                                                                                   org.springframework.ui.Model model)
        Directs the parameters required for deletion of location data to the BootstrapController for deletion of relevant records. After which, users will be redirected back to the same page.
        Parameters:
        macAddress - user's macaddress to be deleted
        startDate - startdate of the deletion period
        starthours - start hour of the deletion period
        startminutes - start minutes of the deletion period
        startseconds - start seconds of the deletion period
        endDate - enddate of the deletion period
        endhours - end hours of the deletion period
        endminutes - end minutes of the deletion period
        endseconds - end seconds of the deletion period
        locationID - locationID records to be deleted
        semanticPlace - semanticPlace records to be deleted
        model -
        Returns:
        String
